  "pageTitle": "紧凑的大件废弃物处理布局",
  "bodyHtml": "<main class=\"product-page case-study-detail-page case-study-detail-page-industrial\">\n      <section class=\"section page-hero\" aria-labelledby=\"case-detail-title\">\n        <p class=\"eyebrow\">大件废弃物箱 详情</p>\n        <h1 id=\"case-detail-title\">紧凑的大件废弃物处理布局</h1>\n        <p class=\"hero-copy\">参考适用于采购方需要在一个工作流程中完成收件、体积缩小、分离和打包废料的紧凑型废弃物预处理。</p>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section case-detail-section case-detail-timeline-section\" id=\"bulky-waste-processing-layout\" aria-labelledby=\"bulky-waste-processing-layout-timeline-title\">\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">参考时间线</p>\n          <h2 id=\"bulky-waste-processing-layout-timeline-title\">从超大垃圾处理到紧凑型预处理</h2>\n          <p>案例按买方评估流程排序：背景、合作单位、限制、解以及对比前后对比。</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"case-detail-timeline\" aria-label=\"案例 详情 时间线\">\n          <article class=\"case-detail-timeline-item\">\n            <div class=\"case-detail-timeline-marker\"><span>01</span></div>\n            <div class=\"case-detail-stage-card\">\n              <p class=\"case-detail-stage-label\">项目背景</p>\n              <h3>超大尺寸混合废物需在处置前进行预处理</h3>\n              <p>该布局通过缩小进料尺寸、分离可回收组分以及准备残渣以便下游处理，处理大件废弃物和轻质混合废物。</p>\n              <dl class=\"case-detail-metrics\">\n                <div><dt>物料类别</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">2 流</strong><span>体积大且轻的混合废弃物</span></dd></div>\n                <div><dt>目标路线</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">1 工作流程</strong><span>接收到打包输出</span></dd></div>\n              </dl>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"case-detail-timeline-item\">\n            <div class=\"case-detail-timeline-marker\"><span>02</span></div>\n            <div class=\"case-detail-stage-card\">\n              <p class=\"case-detail-stage-label\">合作单位</p>\n              <h3>匿名环卫服务运营商</h3>\n              <p>合作单位计划减少大件废弃物运输量，并在最终处置或下游转移前回收可回收组分。</p>\n              <dl class=\"case-detail-metrics\">\n                <div><dt>操作员类型</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">1 环卫团队</strong><span>换乘站运营</span></dd></div>\n                <div><dt>买家关切</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">2 目标</strong><span>减容与回收</span></dd></div>\n              </dl>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"case-detail-timeline-item\">\n            <div class=\"case-detail-timeline-marker\"><span>03</span></div>\n            <div class=\"case-detail-stage-card\">\n              <p class=\"case-detail-stage-label\">实际限制</p>\n              <h3>该布局必须在转运站物流内工作</h3>\n              <p>该场地需要接收区、大型物料分拣区、设备通道、回收分馏物储存区和卡车装载区，且操作空间紧凑。</p>\n              <dl class=\"case-detail-metrics\">\n                <div><dt>场地分区</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">5 区域</strong><span>从货位到装载区</span></dd></div>\n                <div><dt>布局类型</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">紧凑型</strong><span>单一工作流程路径</span></dd></div>\n              </dl>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"case-detail-timeline-item\">\n            <div class=\"case-detail-timeline-marker\"><span>04</span></div>\n            <div class=\"case-detail-stage-card\">\n              <p class=\"case-detail-stage-label\">解决方案</p>\n              <h3>Lion One工艺模块，配套分离和打包接口</h3>\n              <p>工艺范围结合了破碎、筛分、气流分离、输送、可选的磁性分离、打包接口以及远程控制支持。</p>\n              <dl class=\"case-detail-metrics\">\n                <div><dt>流程模块</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">4 模块</strong><span>压碎 / 筛分 / 气流 / 输送</span></dd></div>\n                <div><dt>接口</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">2 接口</strong><span>打包与遥控</span></dd></div>\n              </dl>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"case-detail-timeline-item\">\n            <div class=\"case-detail-timeline-marker\"><span>05</span></div>\n            <div class=\"case-detail-stage-card\">\n              <p class=\"case-detail-stage-label\">前后对比</p>\n              <h3>参考图显示了一条更可控的大件废弃物路线</h3>\n              <div class=\"case-detail-comparison\">\n                <div><span>之前</span><strong>超大废料以松散混合物质的形式流动</strong><p>在缩小尺寸和回收检查前，运输和分级压力一直很高。</p></div>\n                <div><span>之后</span><strong>减容、分离，准备下游处理</strong><p>参考视频展示了送料、破碎、气流分离、排放和打包界面的流程。</p></div>\n              </div>\n              <dl class=\"case-detail-metrics\">\n                <div><dt>视频范围</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">5 步骤</strong><span>进料到打包接口</span></dd></div>\n              </dl>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section case-detail-action-section industrial-rfq-section ai-layout-reference\" aria-label=\"案例操作\">\n        <div class=\"rfq-action-strip case-detail-action-strip\">\n          <a class=\"primary-button\" href=\"/contact\">请求参考包</a>\n          <a class=\"secondary-button\" href=\"/case-studies\">返回案例研究</a>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n    </main>"
}
